These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
House: townhouse, ranch-style
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian
1. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House           | ranch-style | townhouse |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | argentine  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, pineapple
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, trance
1. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Food         | pineapple   | raspberry      |
| Music-Genre   | house | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, february
There 2 different types of food: banana, spinach
1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Birthday   | february | may    |
| Food     | banana | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, british
1. the british is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Flower   | zinnia   | orchid |
| Nationality   | australian | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, project-manager
