.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-6::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, crime
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, airplane
1. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |        2        |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | horror     |
| Transport        | bike | airplane |

