.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Pet   | mouse | guinea-pig |
| Movie-Genre     | disaster   | zombie    |

